n, respectively.\nWe investigate the MT-eQTL model through a simulation study, and rigorously\nestablish the FDR control of the local FDR testing procedure under mild\nassumptions appropriate for dependent data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Nov 2013 21:04:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Dec 2013 20:17:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2015 18:49:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 3 Feb 2016 14:25:32 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 7 Sep 2017 02:56:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-08"}
